value.name: Crash! Insignificant Roommates
value.overview:
It tells the story and episodes of the 10 close boys who have lived together since high school. A group of young boys who find the destination and explore the universe in the early days of university. They were expecting to meet paradise when they entered university. This is a great chance for those who are sad and want to be alone. However, when they started to experience it, they realised that that was not true. They portray the love, friendship, and dreams of the 20s.

A group of boys who face problems in their lives and want to enjoy their life by making friends and girlfriends, but they are wrong.
